{"tid":2497630,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完楚漢驕雄有d疑問","createTime":"2021-04-20T15:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T06:16:43.000Z","uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5032577a0aacb6d5fd8f90c5a015c616bf7a27d0","tid":2497630,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"最中意韓信呢個角色<br />\n諗返起以前睇歷史書d問題<br />\n<br />\n歷史書形容佢成日拎住把劍<br />\n但係秦始皇唔係收天下兵器，點解韓信成日可以拎住把劍？<br />\n<br />\n同埋明明形容佢平民輸到俾人蝦要捲人褲底<br />\n點解佢可以熟讀兵書， 無師自通<br />\n點解佢可以識字？以前平民好難識字同有書<br />\n通常啲書都係要貴族先有得睇<br />\n就當佢成日遊手好閑周圍聽故仔都好難做到用兵如神，上知天文下知地理？ <br />\n<br />\n睇返歷史項羽用兵都好神下，曾經同韓信打成平手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好可惜輸比小人假人既歷史英雄。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好人永遠鬥唔過小人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1c0bf99cbed2ba922db36ef0889ea212544f7e","tid":2497630,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:18:54.000Z","msg":"一:天才<br />\n二:應該係沒落貴族,同埋傳說張良都有高人送書"},{"pid":"559a1f73dd8812a99dbe65900c5a1fdce752b65a","tid":2497630,"uid":345941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"好似係貴族出身"},{"pid":"277ee3b38487a4946ea2f6abbbadd62966e35678","tid":2497630,"uid":185712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:05:08.000Z","msg":"過秦論不可盡信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n篇文係數臭秦 強調仁義 希望漢帝行仁義 <br />\n<br />\n目的係向皇帝sales儒家思想"},{"pid":"e87e4d14f5e9fd6e408029ebcb9cc1644ade7e9c","tid":2497630,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"277ee3b38487a4946ea2f6abbbadd62966e35678","tid":2497630,"uid":185712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:05:08.000Z","msg":"過秦論不可盡信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so